sentence: is there ground . transportation available at the phoenix airport
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.city_code||'"', '"'||v0.transport_type||'"',
 '"'||v2.airport_code||'"', '"'||v3.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.city_name||'"' FROM ground_service v0, airport v1, airport_service v2,
 city v3 
WHERE ((v0.airport_code = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.airport_code = ANY v2.airport_code) 
AND ((v2.city_code = ANY v3.city_code) AND (v3.city_name = 'PHOENIX'))));
